data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Opportunity knocks! This charming, spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in the heart of Palmetto is awaiting your creative touch to restore it to its former glory. Situated on a generous lot, this property offers a private pool, a rare find in this neighborhood, where you can enjoy outdoor relaxation and entertainment.  Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, this home offers easy access to local amenities, schools, parks, and shopping centers. Enjoy the convenience of nearby dining options and a short drive to the Palmetto Riverfront, providing scenic views and recreational opportunities, minutes to I-75 and Bradenton beaches. Perfect for first time home buyer or investor.   Motivated Seller.
